summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to historic preservation, imposing controls upon the Ellsworth Storey Cottages Group, 1706, 1710, 1710 1/2, 1800, 1804, 1808, 1810, 1814 and 1816 Lake Washington Blvd. S., and 1725 and 1729 - 36th Ave. S. Landmarks designated by the Landmarks Preservation Board under Ordinance 106348.
